gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 131, Jazz 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The Lakers defeat the Jazz, 131-99.  Anthony Davis led the way with 26 points and 16 rebounds, while LeBron James added 17 points, 7 rebounds and nine assists in the victory.  Lauri Markkanen tallied 10 points and eight rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort.  The Lakers wrap up their IST group play at 4-0, and are 9-6 on the season, while the Jazz conclude with a 2-2 IST record, sitting 4-10 on the season.
